{"tid":1418834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「前線對街坊要有禮貌」原因好簡單","createTime":"2019-08-05T20:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T15:18:38.000Z","uid":76234,"like":445,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"8b6f5ef4e6999ccfb5bf169404c55eee40c3c008","tid":1418834,"uid":76234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:53:47.000Z","msg":"利申<br />\n放核彈我都唔割<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1）<br />\n公關門面野點都要做d<br />\n<br />\n因為街坊市民好撚表面<br />\n<br />\n對佢地禮貌客氣，條氣就好順<br />\n<br />\n當晒我地係親生仔<br />\n<br />\n有事起上黎<br />\n<br />\n就係佢地幫手屌走d狗！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）<br />\n<br />\n仲有一堆on99 中立 + 淨係睇TVB既平民<br />\n<br />\n如果冇晒街坊係度屌黑警<br />\n<br />\n佢地就會以為TVB 報既野就係事實<br />\n<br />\n會以為我地就係癲撚左既暴徒<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔會見到我地為香港既付出同犧牲<br />\n<br />\n然後就一傳十，十傳百咁snowball落去<br />\n <br />\n咁就變左無撚謂！<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c056c555e09fe3ecc4ec8144c3008fb682ba9224","tid":1418834,"uid":76234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:54:27.000Z","msg":"自己推<br />\n<br />\n推幾野都訓"},{"pid":"38080b2593c708a333e33ed7b77cb4c461b75c54","tid":1418834,"uid":217103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:54:32.000Z","msg":"辛苦大家喇！但我想提返你哋一樣嘢！對市民客氣啲！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418774</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家記得返 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時代革命</span>意思<br />\n點解用時代而唔係世代<br />\n係因為呢個係一整個時代嘅抗爭 <br />\n包咗唔同generation 唔同嘅階層<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港時代革命！</span>"},{"pid":"37d5be7cfad812574debb673cc18795dc027d7fe","tid":1418834,"uid":76234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38080b2593c708a333e33ed7b77cb4c461b75c54","tid":1418834,"uid":217103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:54:32.000Z","msg":"辛苦大家喇！但我想提返你哋一樣嘢！對市民客氣啲！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418774</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家記得返 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時代革命</span>意思<br />\n點解用時代而唔係世代<br />\n係因為呢個係一整個時代嘅抗爭 <br />\n包咗唔同generation 唔同嘅階層<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港時代革命！</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:55:13.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"38f68c58d4b20d2b115548327911c995d348ecf3","tid":1418834,"uid":92500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:55:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ba1498db9c0702ec4a801a3fb69b473f020cc37","tid":1418834,"uid":76234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:56:05.000Z","msg":"推多幾野就訓"},{"pid":"4ed294ae32c7402ad3b9067ab3f8a00eb96263e8","tid":1418834,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73caddb85e7fce28fe9aa284df217b5d93da519e","tid":1418834,"uid":76234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:57:00.000Z","msg":"真係訓"},{"pid":"4ccd94ce9ef80007c5e67a73f988be0b0de144d9","tid":1418834,"uid":76234,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:00:22.000Z","msg":"只有街坊既聲音先可以影響返街坊<br />\n<br />\n只要有禮貌就可以換取一班市民當我地係親生仔<br />\n<br />\n佢地就會多左個理由屌差佬<br />\n<br />\n「因為班示威者對自己有禮貌！佢地唔會係衰人！」"},{"pid":"212476468f68be7365ea98c94efd5482fd09fbbe","tid":1418834,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:02:14.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"a2be257b4507cd83f8814649f9fd97e923b82f11","tid":1418834,"uid":76234,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:03:32.000Z","msg":"真係訓<br />\n<br />\n我cosplay 兩日街坊<br />\n<br />\n深明街坊聲音既影響力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfacebook 流傳既片<br />\n<br />\n發唔發覺永遠最吸睛既都係班「中老年街坊」屌狗片？<br />\n <br />\n因為佢地既聲音<br />\n<br />\n代表左出黎抗爭既人，對政府不滿既人<br />\n<br />\n唔止得後生仔！！！"},{"pid":"59c317dcf6a4e6d7dd96d4d709e6c474597b172e","tid":1418834,"uid":122083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:04:08.000Z","msg":"真係要有禮貌啲<br />\n人地無出手打人或者拎武器之前<br />\n都應該當佢係普通市民<br />\n最近見到幾次屌錯人<br />\n將心比己有時啲人俾你咁屌<br />\n就算本身無野都想同你鬥氣<br />\n唔好自動標籤左人先<br />\n我明白有時好嬲好多野想做<br />\n但係市民唔係我地既敵人<br />\n唔好主動攻擊人 無論口定手"},{"pid":"626f280d59adad0118261e8d7664f1847fb2203c","tid":1418834,"uid":76234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:04:37.000Z","msg":"各位加油！<br />\n<br />\n核彈都唔割！"},{"pid":"12fab61608b522f896d6474983f7d917ea2fea50","tid":1418834,"uid":125542,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:06:06.000Z","msg":"啱呀 前線真係唔可以再咁衝動<br />\n我地要對準政權 <br />\n火魔法師玩警察都唔緊要 但係唔好亂屌街坊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c59ac5e52a9d33260a3edd6b2afb97b536a5f86","tid":1418834,"uid":270871,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:06:10.000Z","msg":"屌影相其實唔係好關前唔前線事<br />\n反而前線戴晒豬咀好難嗌得大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdd2b8b8745dd0ca0a9aaa2bfcc53c73ced90ad","tid":1418834,"uid":125542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:06:17.000Z","msg":"對準政權呀"},{"pid":"d358f019fbff46b3b49df33b238c9fede87e4843","tid":1418834,"uid":76234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59c317dcf6a4e6d7dd96d4d709e6c474597b172e","tid":1418834,"uid":122083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:04:08.000Z","msg":"真係要有禮貌啲<br />\n人地無出手打人或者拎武器之前<br />\n都應該當佢係普通市民<br />\n最近見到幾次屌錯人<br />\n將心比己有時啲人俾你咁屌<br />\n就算本身無野都想同你鬥氣<br />\n唔好自動標籤左人先<br />\n我明白有時好嬲好多野想做<br />\n但係市民唔係我地既敵人<br />\n唔好主動攻擊人 無論口定手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:06:21.000Z","msg":"每多一個街坊幫口屌<br />\n<br />\n影響到既同區廢中老就多幾十個"},{"pid":"a272e06b0e6a019d3dfd810518ca5ce3f78c122e","tid":1418834,"uid":19540